---
import MainHead from "../components/MainHead.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<MainHead
			title="About | Manuel Thomsen"
			description="About Manuel Thomsen Lorem Ipsum"
		/>
		<style>
			.heroImg {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				max-height: 100%;
				object-fit: contain;
				overflow: hidden;
			}
			.portrait {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 20em;
				mix-blend-mode: multiply;
			}

			.heroImg img {
				position: relative;
				width: 100%;
			}

			.bio {
				font-size: var(--f-u1);
				line-height: 2;
				margin-top: 4em;
			}

			.wrapper.bio {
				max-width: 50em;
				padding: 0;
			}
			.quote {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				margin-top: 4em;
			}
			.quote p {
				color: var(--hidden-love);
				
				font-size: var(--f-u1);
				font-weight: 800;
				line-height: 2;
			}
			.link {
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: var(--f-d1);
		padding-top: 0.75em;
	}
	.link-underlined {
		border-radius: 2px;		
		display: inline-block;
		position: relative;
		color: #0087ca;
	}
	.link-underlined::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		width: 100%;
		transform: scaleX(0);
		height: 2px;
		bottom: 0;
		left: 0;
		background-color: #0087ca;
		transform-origin: bottom right;
		transition: transform 0.25s ease-out;
	}
	.link-underlined:hover::after {
		transform: scaleX(1);
  		transform-origin: bottom left;
	}

	.link:hover,
	.link:focus {
		
	}
			.Hi {
				background-color: #22222255;
				background-blend-mode: multiply;
				color: white;
				position: absolute;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 2rem;
			}
			@media (min-width: 750px) {

				.Hi {
					font-size: 4rem;
				}

				.quote {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: row;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				margin-top: 4em;
			}
			.quote p {
				
				margin-left: 2em;
				font-size: var(--f-u1);
				font-weight: 800;
				line-height: 2;
			}
			}
				
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Nav />
		<div class="wrapper">
			<h1>About Me</h1>
			<div class="heroImg">
				<span class="Hi">&nbsp&nbsp Hi there!üôã‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è &nbsp&nbsp</span>
				<video
					loop
					muted
					autoplay
					width="100%"
					height="auto"
					src="assets/product.mp4"></video>
			</div>
			<div class="bio wrapper">
				<p>
					Welcome! I'm <span class="link link-underlined">Manuel</span>, a software developer driven by the desire to create innovative and user-friendly digital products. My expertise lies in developing solutions that are not only seamless in functionality but also visually captivating. With a strong background in both software development and creative production, I'm well-equipped to tailor products to my clients' unique needs. <br />
					<br />
					I am dedicated to pushing the boundaries of digital product development by staying abreast of the latest technologies and techniques. Outside of work, my passion for 3D design and motion graphics keeps me exploring and growing. Whether it's working with Blender or Adobe After Effects, I continuously seek ways to create functional and visually striking digital products. <br />
				</p>
				<div class="quote">
					<img class="portrait" src="/assets/manuel.png" alt="">
					<p>
						If you have an intriguing idea for an AI, AR, or 3D project, I'd love to hear about it! I'm always up for a challenge and eager to collaborate with like-minded individuals who share my enthusiasm for innovation.
					</p>
				
					
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- 2 col responsive div with text on the left and an image on the right -->
			

		</div>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
